ef><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wcpo.com/news/local-news/butler-county/middletown/ron-howard-is-back-in-middletown-the-setting-of-upcoming-hillbilly-elegy-adaptation|title=Ron Howard is back in Middletown, the setting of upcoming 'Hillbilly Elegy' adaptation|date=2019-03-25|website=WCPO|access-date=2019-03-27|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327043525/https://www.wcpo.com/news/local-news/butler-county/middletown/ron-howard-is-back-in-middletown-the-setting-of-upcoming-hillbilly-elegy-adaptation|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

