==评价==
=== 专业评价 ===
尽管影片口碑较差，部分演员的表现还是获得了肯定<ref name=slash>{{cite web|last=Bui|first=Hoai-Tran|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/hillbilly-elegy-reviews-round-up/|title='Hillbilly Elegy' Review Round-Up: Ron Howard's Shameless Oscar Bait Drama is Very, Very Bad|access-date=2020-11-16|date=2020-11-10|work=Slash Film|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112032253/https://www.slashfilm.com/hillbilly-elegy-reviews-round-up/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Rawat|first=Kshitij|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/hollywood/hillbilly-elegy-review-roundup-critics-pan-glenn-close-amy-adams-starrer-7049140/|title=Hillbilly Elegy review roundup: Critics pan Glenn Close and Amy Adams-starrer|access-date=2020-11-16|date=2020-11-12|work=The Indian Express|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118134757/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/hollywood/hillbilly-elegy-review-roundup-critics-pan-glenn-close-amy-adams-starrer-7049140/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]录得245条评论，拿下26%的腐烂度，平均得分4.60/10。网站共识写道：“《乡下人的悲歌》在采用了有希望在颁奖季获奖的格式，但内核是平淡无奇的情节剧，这让几位非常优秀演员在[[美国深南部|不那么深的南部]]犯了难<ref name=RT>{{cite web|title=Hillbilly Elegy (2020)|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hillbilly_elegy|website=Rotten Tomatoes|access-date=2021-03-18|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127091539/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hillbilly_elegy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]收录43条评论，平均得分38/100，即“普遍差评”<ref name=Meta>{{cite web|title=Hillbilly Elegy Reviews|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/hillbilly-elegy|website=Metacritic|access-date=2020-12-18|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119185343/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/hillbilly-elegy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[独立报|独立报]]》分析，影片之所以遭遇广泛批评，是因为“延续了对贫困群体的刻板印象”<ref>{{cite web|first=Ellie|last=Harrison|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/amy-adams-hillbilly-elegy-bad-reviews-b1762696.html|title=Hillbilly Elegy: Amy Adams responds to bad reviews of ‘sickeningly irresponsible’ film|access-date=2020-11-29|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129231350/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/amy-adams-hillbilly-elegy-bad-reviews-b1762696.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[影音俱乐部|影音俱乐部]]》的凯蒂·瑞夫（Katie Rife）认为影片是“自成一派的{{le|穷苦影像|poverty porn}}”，意在“放大强化一些刻板印象”<ref name="May ''Hillbilly Elegy'' mark the end of Trump-era myth-making about the white working class">{{cite web|last=Rife|first=Katie|title="May ''Hillbilly Elegy'' mark the end of Trump-era myth-making about the white working class"|url=https://film.avclub.com/may-hillbilly-elegy-mark-the-end-of-trump-era-myth-maki-1845625283|website=The A.V. Club|access-date=2020-09-10|date=2020-09-10|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110193724/https://film.avclub.com/may-hillbilly-elegy-mark-the-end-of-trump-era-myth-maki-1845625283|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的{{tsl|en|Owen Gleiberman|欧文·格里伯曼}}表示，“只要克洛斯的表演能获得如潮好评（她的表演实际上也是相当细腻），《乡下人的悲歌》就永远不会过时。艾米·亚当斯贡献了一些教科书级别的表演，但也正因为她的演技太过于娴熟，我们无法用怜悯和恐惧的态度去看待阿贝这个角色”<ref>{{cite web|date=2020-11-10|last=Gleiberman|first=Owen|title='Hillbilly Elegy' Review: Amy Adams and Glenn Close Act with Down-Home Flamboyance in Ron Howard's Otherwise Overly Safe Adaptation|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/hillbilly-elegy-review-amy-adams-glenn-close-ron-howard-jd-vance-1234826719/|work=Variety|access-date=2020-11-10|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110140127/https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/hillbilly-elegy-review-amy-adams-glenn-close-ron-howard-jd-vance-1234826719/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]的大卫·埃尔利希（David Ehrlich）给出“C–”的评价，认为影片“围绕着玛摩的愿望展开，也就是脱离亲人总比寻亲好。万斯的故事很明显在影片开头就已经完满结束，因为他的愿望已经实现。而且影片讲述他逐渐走出阴霾，重燃步向成功的这个过程，让人感到非常失望，有点社交病的意味<ref>{{cite news|last=Ehrlich|first=David|title='Hillbilly Elegy' Review: Ron Howard Adapts J.D. Vance's Controversial Memoir into a Forgettable Netflix Biopic|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/11/hillbilly-elegy-review-netflix-1234597691/|date=2020-11-10|work=IndieWire|access-date=2020-11-10|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110140219/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/11/hillbilly-elegy-review-netflix-1234597691/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

《[[早安美国|早安美国]]》的[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]认为影片“错失良机”，不过克洛斯的表演“非常出色”。他表示：“《乡下人的悲歌》不想落入好莱坞的范式，过分强调简约，让它不仅仅错失了机会<ref>{{cite web|last=America|first=Good Morning|title=Review: 'Hillbilly Elegy' is a 'missed opportunity'; Glenn Close is 'sensational'|url=https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/hillbilly-elegy-review-missed-opportunity-featuring-sensational-glenn-74299301|access-date=2020-11-25|website=Good Morning America|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123084303/https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/hillbilly-elegy-review-missed-opportunity-featuring-sensational-glenn-74299301|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[雪梨晨鋒報|雪梨晨鋒報]]》的桑德拉·霍尔（Sandra Hall）赞赏霍华德的“高端商业片制作品牌”，认为他邀请克洛斯出演，让她用丰富的想象力和演技，向我们展示她的全副才能，理应受到表扬<ref>{{cite web|last=Hall|first=Sandra|date=2020-11-18|title=Is Hillbilly Elegy poverty porn or a masterclass by Ron Howard?|url=https://www.smh.com.au/culture/movies/is-hillbilly-elegy-poverty-porn-or-a-masterclass-by-ron-howard-20201118-p56fq6.html|access-date=2020-11-25|website=The Sydney Morning Herald|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124202712/https://www.smh.com.au/culture/movies/is-hillbilly-elegy-poverty-porn-or-a-masterclass-by-ron-howard-20201118-p56fq6.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的{{tsl|en|Richard Roeper|理查德·罗珀}}给出4星满分评价，赞扬亚当斯和克洛斯的“出色表现”，认为亚当斯“了不起”，克洛斯“表演精湛、控制全场、表现出色”<ref>{{cite web|last=Times|first=Chicago Sun|title=Review: 'Hillbilly Elegy' a sure bet for Oscar love, and deservedly so|url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/movies-and-tv/2020/11/10/21557633/hillbilly-elegy-review-amy-adams-glenn-close-movie|access-date=2021-02-04|website=Chicago Sun-Times|archive-date=2020-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229203824/https://chicago.suntimes.com/movies-and-tv/2020/11/10/21557633/hillbilly-elegy-review-amy-adams-glenn-close-movie|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Film Companion|Film Companion}}的拉胡尔·德赛（Rahul Desai）认为影片“厚颜无耻地蹭了奥斯卡的热度”。从朗·霍华德最近大部分作品来看，他有把“烂片拍好的能力”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.filmcompanion.in/reviews/hollywood-review/hillbilly-elegy-netflix-review-veers-between-american-caricature-and-universal-soul-amy-adams-ron-howard-rahul-desai/?utm_source=Wikipedia&utm_medium=Seeding&utm_campaign=Reviews|title=Hillbilly Elegy Review|first=Rahul|last=Desai|date=2020-11-24|work=Film Companion|access-date=2020-11-25|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204230030/https://www.filmcompanion.in/reviews/hollywood-review/hillbilly-elegy-netflix-review-veers-between-american-caricature-and-universal-soul-amy-adams-ron-howard-rahul-desai/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

